7
00:01:48,480 --> 00:01:49,479
It invigorates the spleen
and dispels dampness.

8
00:01:49,520 --> 00:01:50,757
It's helpful against this illness.

9
00:01:50,878 --> 00:01:52,358
I'll organise it into an article

10
00:01:52,438 --> 00:01:54,504
and publish it on
the public account right away.

11
00:02:07,198 --> 00:02:08,198
I'm not

12
00:02:09,318 --> 00:02:10,557
having coronavirus, am I?

13
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:14,459
What you have is
more serious than coronavirus.

14
00:02:21,670 --> 00:02:22,470
Drink your medicine.

15
00:02:24,440 --> 00:02:25,280
Thank you, my wife.

16
00:02:33,597 --> 00:02:35,078
Easy, easy.

17
00:02:37,757 --> 00:02:38,557
Okay.

18
00:02:48,478 --> 00:02:50,517
Are all the other matters
arranged properly?

19
