as many patients as possible.

20
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:56,080
It's all arranged,

21
00:02:56,200 --> 00:02:58,200
so things are not as tense on our end.

22
00:02:58,884 --> 00:02:59,684
However,

23
00:03:00,224 --> 00:03:01,343
most patients

24
00:03:01,570 --> 00:03:03,131
don't understand our approach.

25
00:03:03,837 --> 00:03:04,637
After all,

26
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:05,801
families have to be

27
00:03:06,091 --> 00:03:07,171
quarantined separately.

28
00:03:08,551 --> 00:03:10,204
They would be worried about each other.

29
00:03:11,158 --> 00:03:12,277
In special times,

30
00:03:13,158 --> 00:03:14,197
we need special measures.

31
00:03:18,009 --> 00:03:19,369
Isn't our family

32
00:03:20,276 --> 00:03:21,356
doing the same?

33
00:03:27,320 --> 00:03:28,320
Ouch, ouch.

34
00:03:28,864 --> 00:03:29,744
Ouch, ouch

35
00:03:31,289 --> 00:03:32,130
Don't move.

36
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:34,040
If this abscess doesn't heal,

37
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:36,360
you will suffer in your later years,
you know?

38
00:03:36,433 --> 00:03:37,233
It's fine.

39
00:03:38,038 --> 00:03:39,038
In my later years,

40
00:03:39,643 --> 00:03:40,949
I have you to take care of me.

41
00:03:42,621 --> 00:03:44,473
Where do you get the confidence
to say that?

42
00:03:45,844 --> 00:03:46,644
I know.

43
00:03:48,798 --> 00:03:49,757
You can't bear...

44
