00:36:14,598 --> 00:36:16,038
Our son won't.

582
00:36:17,397 --> 00:36:18,197
He really

583
00:36:18,964 --> 00:36:20,837
looks like a doctor now.

584
00:36:20,983 --> 00:36:21,783
Yes.

585
00:36:22,637 --> 00:36:24,877
Through this epidemic, I've seen it.

586
00:36:25,677 --> 00:36:26,677
This kid

587
00:36:28,318 --> 00:36:29,844
is cut out to be a TCM practitioner.

588
00:36:30,637 --> 00:36:32,038
His pure heart

589
00:36:32,118 --> 00:36:33,397
matches his name,

590
00:36:34,477 --> 00:36:35,278
Tian Zhen.

591
00:36:36,318 --> 00:36:37,118
I know, right?

592
00:36:55,877 --> 00:36:56,758
Let me ask you.

593
00:36:57,877 --> 00:36:59,397
Have you ever

594
00:37:01,598 --> 00:37:02,637
had feelings

595
00:37:03,838 --> 00:37:04,798
for Little Lark?

596
00:37:06,637 --> 00:37:08,397
You know, like a secret crush.

597
00:37:09,038 --> 00:37:09,917
Even Dad said

598
00:37:10,030 --> 00:37:10,910
that you and her

599
00:37:11,038 --> 00:37:12,877
were evenly matched in your class.

600
00:37:13,118 --> 00:37:14,798
Wu Shan Dao was even a bit behind her.

601
00:37:16,197 --> 00:37:17,477
That's narrow-minded.

602
00:37:20,118 --> 00:37:23,358
Do you think there's only romantic
love between a man and a woman?

603
00:37:24,637 --> 00:37:26,336
There's also another kind of connection,

604
00:37:27,558 --> 00:37:29,397
a mutual appreciation.

605
00:37:29,969 --> 00:37:31,209
Come on,

606
00:37:31,397 --> 00:37:33,077
