607
00:37:33,157 --> 00:37:34,957
What mutual appreciation?

608
00:37:36,358 --> 00:37:37,397
I've been thinking,

609
00:37:39,276 --> 00:37:40,117
if I didn't

610
00:37:40,598 --> 00:37:41,838
have feelings

611
00:37:42,358 --> 00:37:44,078
for someone else back then,

612
00:37:44,757 --> 00:37:46,158
given my mistakes,

613
00:37:47,437 --> 00:37:48,278
I should have...

614
00:37:49,157 --> 00:37:50,329
I should have married her.

615
00:37:51,637 --> 00:37:53,637
She wouldn't have ended up

616
00:37:54,157 --> 00:37:55,038
alone until now.

617
00:37:59,520 --> 00:38:00,320
Ren Xin Zheng,

618
00:38:01,598 --> 00:38:02,917
come clean now.

619
00:38:03,798 --> 00:38:05,717
How many women are there in your heart?

620
00:38:06,118 --> 00:38:07,651
Who else did you have feelings for?

621
00:38:10,477 --> 00:38:11,716
I don't dare to say anymore.

622
00:38:13,118 --> 00:38:13,918
Tell me!

623
00:38:14,637 --> 00:38:15,598
Tell me!

624
00:38:18,877 --> 00:38:20,477
Stop trying to scare me by coughing.

625
00:38:22,917 --> 00:38:23,717
Have some water.

626
00:38:45,677 --> 00:38:47,518
Do you remember

627
00:38:47,598 --> 00:38:49,038
where we first met?

628
00:38:49,157 --> 00:38:50,358
Of course I remember.

629
00:38:50,760 --> 00:38:52,081
You always forget,

630
00:38:52,197 --> 00:38:54,163
saying that it was
during our university days.

631
00:38:55,397 --> 00:38:57,318
Actually, I noticed you
long before that.

