00:39:07,250 --> 00:39:08,676
I was in high school at that time.

636
00:39:09,038 --> 00:39:12,677
The first time we met was at the school.

637
00:39:13,677 --> 00:39:15,558
Not when you started school,

638
00:39:16,263 --> 00:39:18,144
but when I started university.

639
00:39:20,318 --> 00:39:21,197
I think

640
00:39:22,078 --> 00:39:23,397
at that time,

641
00:39:24,598 --> 00:39:26,864
you must have been in
your first senior year of high school.

642
00:39:28,038 --> 00:39:29,558
You were wearing a blue dress.

643
00:39:43,598 --> 00:39:45,317
Lan Lan!

644
00:39:45,397 --> 00:39:47,118
-Make way!
-Slow down!

645
00:39:49,038 --> 00:39:50,397
Unbelievable!

646
00:39:50,477 --> 00:39:51,918
Slow down! Be careful!

647
00:39:52,558 --> 00:39:53,750
Careful not to hit someone!

648
00:39:56,118 --> 00:39:56,918
You...

649
00:39:59,318 --> 00:40:00,557
Move! Move!

650
00:40:00,637 --> 00:40:01,598
Don't ride so fast!

651
00:40:03,397 --> 00:40:04,918
Move! Move!

652
00:40:06,477 --> 00:40:07,277
Watch out!

653
00:40:22,040 --> 00:40:24,877
Why haven't I seen you wearing
the blue dress again after that?

654
00:40:28,237 --> 00:40:29,037
Oh, right.

655
00:40:29,397 --> 00:40:31,197
Where did that blue dress go?

656
00:40:31,516 --> 00:40:33,157
How come I couldn't find it later?

657
00:40:34,838 --> 00:40:37,118
Why did you only tell me this now?

658
00:40:37,717 --> 00:40:39,950
Were you planning
to keep it a secret from me forever?

659
00:40:42,250 --> 00:40:44,331
We need to save our trump cards

660
00:40:45,038 --> 00:40:46,717
for critical moments.

661
00:40:48,598 --> 00:40:50,477
You're just too cunning.

662
00:40:51,078 --> 00:40:52,917
What's wrong with being cunning?

663
00:40:53,200 --> 00:40:54,321
Unlike you,

664
00:40:55,078 --> 00:40:57,598
whose mind is so easy to read.

665
00:40:58,909 --> 00:40:59,710
Now you understand

666
00:40:59,798 --> 00:41:02,118
why your father passed on
the position to me

667
00:41:02,796 --> 00:41:04,117
instead of you, right?

668
00:41:04,303 --> 00:41:05,624
You women

669
00:41:06,078 --> 00:41:09,477
