670
00:41:10,237 --> 00:41:11,358
Do you love me?

671
00:41:11,637 --> 00:41:13,238
Tell me! Tell me!

672
00:41:13,318 --> 00:41:14,638
Tell me! Tell me!

673
00:41:16,637 --> 00:41:18,677
Actually, I'm confessing my love to you

674
00:41:19,397 --> 00:41:21,078
with my whole life.

675
00:41:27,877 --> 00:41:28,838
Do you understand now?

676
00:41:29,637 --> 00:41:31,136
You don't feel jealous now, do you?

677
00:41:32,677 --> 00:41:34,078
Am I the jealous one?

678
00:41:35,038 --> 00:41:35,838
I am.

679
00:41:39,917 --> 00:41:42,157
Now, I have to tell you
about another thing

680
00:41:43,118 --> 00:41:44,957
