681
00:41:46,877 --> 00:41:48,798
There aren't so
many unhappy things in life.

682
00:41:49,490 --> 00:41:51,091
It's all happy things. Happy things.

683
00:41:52,157 --> 00:41:54,837
Life has a way
of slapping you in the face,

684
00:41:54,917 --> 00:41:56,518
reminding you

685
00:41:56,798 --> 00:41:59,558
