you have.

686
00:42:00,318 --> 00:42:01,637
Let it slap, let it be.

687
00:42:02,157 --> 00:42:03,077
With you by my side,

688
00:42:03,157 --> 00:42:05,637
I have a suit of armour.

689
00:42:07,157 --> 00:42:08,637
Life's default setting

690
00:42:09,237 --> 00:42:11,318
