692
00:42:13,798 --> 00:42:15,238
When you embrace something joyful,

693
00:42:15,318 --> 00:42:17,717
there's always something sad
waiting for you.

694
00:42:19,330 --> 00:42:20,949
There aren't that many sad things.

695
00:42:21,080 --> 00:42:22,760
When you have the love of your life,

696
00:42:22,823 --> 00:42:23,903
it's all joy.

697
00:42:25,957 --> 00:42:27,717
You no longer doubt

698
00:42:28,118 --> 00:42:29,717
that Tou Tou is my daughter,

